{
  "video_id": "AQSGyV0rh5Y",
  "title": "Robot therapists - 6 Minute English",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 7540.0,
      "end_time": 9160.0,
      "text": "Catherine: Welcome to 6 Minute English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 9360.0,
      "end_time": 11580.0,
      "text": "the programme where we explore an interesting"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 11700.0,
      "end_time": 14979.0,
      "text": "topic and bring you six items of useful vocabulary."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 14980.0,
      "end_time": 16120.0,
      "text": "I'm Catherine."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16239.0,
      "end_time": 17119.0,
      "text": "Rob: And I'm Rob."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17360.0,
      "end_time": 19000.0,
      "text": "Catherine: I have a question for you, Rob:"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19340.0,
      "end_time": 22280.0,
      "text": "how would you feel about having therapy"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 22500.0,
      "end_time": 23600.0,
      "text": "from a robot?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 23940.0,
      "end_time": 25420.0,
      "text": "Rob: I'm not too sure about that -"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25620.0,
      "end_time": 28140.0,
      "text": "you'll need to tell me more! But first things first,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 28380.0,
      "end_time": 32140.0,
      "text": "the word therapy refers to a kind of treatment that helps"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 32140.0,
      "end_time": 33860.0,
      "text": "someone feel better - including"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 34000.0,
      "end_time": 35660.0,
      "text": "treatment for mental health issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 35960.0,
      "end_time": 38760.0,
      "text": "Someone who delivers therapy is called a therapist."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 39100.0,
      "end_time": 41720.0,
      "text": "Catherine: We'll find out more about this robot therapist"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 41720.0,
      "end_time": 44199.0,
      "text": "in just a moment, but first, Rob,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 44420.0,
      "end_time": 47600.0,
      "text": "I've got a question for you about the scale"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 47600.0,
      "end_time": 49380.0,
      "text": "of mental health issues globally."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 49620.0,
      "end_time": 53739.0,
      "text": "So roughly how many people do you think experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 53740.0,
      "end_time": 56180.0,
      "text": "mental health issues at some point during"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 56340.0,
      "end_time": 60940.0,
      "text": "their lifetime? Is it... a) One in ten people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 60940.0,
      "end_time": 65140.0,
      "text": "b) One in four or c) One in three"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 65340.0,
      "end_time": 66520.0,
      "text": "Rob: I'll go for one in four,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 66520.0,
      "end_time": 68820.0,
      "text": "but I know whichever answer is right -"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 68820.0,
      "end_time": 69820.0,
      "text": "it's a big issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 70100.0,
      "end_time": 71919.0,
      "text": "How might a robot therapist help?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 71930.0,
      "end_time": 73720.0,
      "text": "Catherine: We're not talking about a robot"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 73720.0,
      "end_time": 76740.0,
      "text": "in the Star Wars sense - so there's no flashing"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 76820.0,
      "end_time": 80259.0,
      "text": "lights and mechanical arms, Rob! It's actually an app"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 82640.0,
      "text": "in your smartphone that talks to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 83800.0,
      "end_time": 85620.0,
      "text": "- and it's called Woebot."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 85800.0,
      "end_time": 87720.0,
      "text": "Rob: So - it has a sense of humour."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 88600.0,
      "end_time": 91460.0,
      "text": "Woe means 'sadness'; so this is a 'woe' bot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 91460.0,
      "end_time": 92679.0,
      "text": "not a robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 93800.0,
      "end_time": 95220.0,
      "text": "Catherine: And it was developed by psychologist"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 95440.0,
      "end_time": 98520.0,
      "text": "Dr Alison Darcy from Stanford University"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 98780.0,
      "end_time": 102800.0,
      "text": "in the US. Here she is talking to the BBC radio"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 102800.0,
      "end_time": 103720.0,
      "text": "programme All in the Mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 104100.0,
      "end_time": 106100.0,
      "text": "Dr Alison Darcy: Well, after you start an"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 107420.0,
      "text": "initial conversation with the Woebot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107420.0,
      "end_time": 108960.0,
      "text": "and he'll take you through sort of what he can do"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 108960.0,
      "end_time": 110779.0,
      "text": "and what he can't do, he'll just essentially"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 110780.0,
      "end_time": 112980.0,
      "text": "check in with you every day and just give you"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 112980.0,
      "end_time": 114500.0,
      "text": "a sort of figurative tap on the shoulder"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 114740.0,
      "end_time": 117119.0,
      "text": "and say: \"Hey Claudia, how are you doing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 117120.0,
      "end_time": 118700.0,
      "text": "What's going on in your day? How do you feel?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 118820.0,
      "end_time": 121259.0,
      "text": "So if you say, like \"I'm really, really stressed out\","
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 121600.0,
      "end_time": 123940.0,
      "text": "Woebot might offer to help"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 124600.0,
      "end_time": 125220.0,
      "text": "talk you through something."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 126220.0,
      "end_time": 128479.0,
      "text": "Catherine: Woebot checks in with you every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 128660.0,
      "end_time": 130259.0,
      "text": "and asks how you are."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 130500.0,
      "end_time": 132340.0,
      "text": "Rob: So here, to check in with someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 132620.0,
      "end_time": 135200.0,
      "text": "doesn't mean to register at a hotel with that person!"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 135520.0,
      "end_time": 138800.0,
      "text": "It's an informal way of saying you talk to someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 138120.0,
      "end_time": 140580.0,
      "text": "in order to report or find out information."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 140820.0,
      "end_time": 143760.0,
      "text": "Catherine: And this usage is more common in the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 143760.0,
      "end_time": 146179.0,
      "text": "So for example: \"I can't meet you today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 148320.0,
      "text": "Rob, but I'll check in with you tomorrow"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 148320.0,
      "end_time": 149959.0,
      "text": "to see how the project is getting on.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 150200.0,
      "end_time": 153239.0,
      "text": "Rob: So, this robot checks in with you every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 153240.0,
      "end_time": 155240.0,
      "text": "It tracks your mood and talks to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 155300.0,
      "end_time": 157300.0,
      "text": "about your emotions, using a technique"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 157600.0,
      "end_time": 159900.0,
      "text": "called cognitive behavioural therapy."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 160100.0,
      "end_time": 162400.0,
      "text": "Catherine: Cognitive behavioural therapy"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 162500.0,
      "end_time": 164620.0,
      "text": "is a common therapeutic technique"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 164780.0,
      "end_time": 166780.0,
      "text": "that helps people deal with problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 166960.0,
      "end_time": 168960.0,
      "text": "by changing the way they think."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 169140.0,
      "end_time": 170179.0,
      "text": "Rob: That all sounds great,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 170320.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "but does Woebot actually work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 172540.0,
      "end_time": 174359.0,
      "text": "Catherine: They've done trials which show that"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 174360.0,
      "end_time": 176820.0,
      "text": "it can be more effective than simply reading"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 176920.0,
      "end_time": 178720.0,
      "text": "information about mental health."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 178720.0,
      "end_time": 181960.0,
      "text": "But they haven't compared Woebot to a real"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 182160.0,
      "end_time": 184820.0,
      "text": "therapist due to ethical concerns."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 185400.0,
      "end_time": 187220.0,
      "text": "Rob: Yes, it could be unethical to deny"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 187420.0,
      "end_time": 189720.0,
      "text": "a real patient access to a human therapist"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 189720.0,
      "end_time": 191720.0,
      "text": "for the sake of a trial."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 191740.0,
      "end_time": 194240.0,
      "text": "Ethical basically means morally right."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 194440.0,
      "end_time": 196800.0,
      "text": "Catherine: And another concern is privacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 197600.0,
      "end_time": 200800.0,
      "text": "People who use apps like this are not protected"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 200320.0,
      "end_time": 202400.0,
      "text": "by strong privacy laws."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 202240.0,
      "end_time": 204420.0,
      "text": "Rob: Despite these fears, digital therapy"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 204580.0,
      "end_time": 206940.0,
      "text": "is booming - and Woebot is just one of an"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 207000.0,
      "end_time": 209360.0,
      "text": "an increasing number of electronic services."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 209880.0,
      "end_time": 212480.0,
      "text": "One reason for this could be using an app carries less"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 212520.0,
      "end_time": 215600.0,
      "text": "stigma than maybe seeing a human therapist."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 215400.0,
      "end_time": 217440.0,
      "text": "Catherine: And stigma refers to the negative"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 217580.0,
      "end_time": 220160.0,
      "text": "associations that people have about something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 220320.0,
      "end_time": 223220.0,
      "text": "especially when these associations are not fair."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 223680.0,
      "end_time": 225680.0,
      "text": "Even though mental health is now being"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 225820.0,
      "end_time": 227959.0,
      "text": "talked about more openly than before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 228440.0,
      "end_time": 231780.0,
      "text": "some people do still see mental health issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 231920.0,
      "end_time": 233519.0,
      "text": "and therapy negatively."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 233900.0,
      "end_time": 236100.0,
      "text": "Rob: Whatever you think of robot therapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 236340.0,
      "end_time": 238460.0,
      "text": "Dr Darcy believes that in the modern world"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 238700.0,
      "end_time": 240720.0,
      "text": "people need to self-reflect more -"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 240900.0,
      "end_time": 243160.0,
      "text": "which means thinking deeply about yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 243360.0,
      "end_time": 245840.0,
      "text": "in order to understand the reasons behind your feelings."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 246480.0,
      "end_time": 247720.0,
      "text": "Dr Alison Darcy: The world that we live in right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 247840.0,
      "end_time": 250300.0,
      "text": "is very noisy. Particularly digitally."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 250560.0,
      "end_time": 253220.0,
      "text": "You know, since we've had these little computers"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 253420.0,
      "end_time": 255420.0,
      "text": "in our pockets with us everywhere we go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 255760.0,
      "end_time": 258700.0,
      "text": "there aren't that many opportunities for real silence"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 258700.0,
      "end_time": 261159.0,
      "text": "or self-reflection. You know, even a commute"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 261320.0,
      "end_time": 263440.0,
      "text": "on the tube might have been a moment to"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 263440.0,
      "end_time": 266820.0,
      "text": "just take a second to yourself, but now that void"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 266820.0,
      "end_time": 269800.0,
      "text": "can be filled always with super engaging content"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 269800.0,
      "end_time": 271200.0,
      "text": "by looking at your phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 271440.0,
      "end_time": 273800.0,
      "text": "Catherine: Darcy believes that we don't have"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 273800.0,
      "end_time": 274859.0,
      "text": "much time for self-reflection"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 275100.0,
      "end_time": 277500.0,
      "text": "because there are so many distractions in life -"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 277500.0,
      "end_time": 279440.0,
      "text": "especially smartphones!"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 279440.0,
      "end_time": 282200.0,
      "text": "Rob: After discussing all this - would you actually try"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 282160.0,
      "end_time": 283580.0,
      "text": "a therapy app like this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 283920.0,
      "end_time": 284880.0,
      "text": "Catherine: Yes I would, actually -"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 284880.0,
      "end_time": 286580.0,
      "text": "I think it might be quite helpful."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 286580.0,
      "end_time": 287940.0,
      "text": "Rob: And how about the question you asked me"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 287940.0,
      "end_time": 289500.0,
      "text": "at the beginning of the programme: how"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 289500.0,
      "end_time": 292250.0,
      "text": "many people experience mental health issues?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 292720.0,
      "end_time": 294680.0,
      "text": "Catherine: The answer was: one in four,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 294680.0,
      "end_time": 297220.0,
      "text": "according the World Health Organisation"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 297440.0,
      "end_time": 299640.0,
      "text": "and the World Federation for Mental Health."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 299960.0,
      "end_time": 303280.0,
      "text": "But the WHO say that as many as two-thirds"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 303520.0,
      "end_time": 306340.0,
      "text": "of people never seek help from a health professional -"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 306520.0,
      "end_time": 309460.0,
      "text": "with stigma being one of the main reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 309780.0,
      "end_time": 311900.0,
      "text": "Rob: And just there we had stigma again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 312260.0,
      "end_time": 314620.0,
      "text": "let's now run through the other words we learned today."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 314800.0,
      "end_time": 317640.0,
      "text": "Catherine: So we had woe meaning sadness."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 317880.0,
      "end_time": 321300.0,
      "text": "I'm full of woe. Woe is me!"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 321520.0,
      "end_time": 322919.0,
      "text": "Rob: Maybe you need some therapy -"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 323600.0,
      "end_time": 325720.0,
      "text": "that's the process of receiving treatment for a particular"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 325920.0,
      "end_time": 328360.0,
      "text": "health issue, especially mental health illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 328620.0,
      "end_time": 330940.0,
      "text": "Catherine: And we had - to check in with someone."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 331200.0,
      "end_time": 333800.0,
      "text": "After we finish this programme, I need to check in with"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 333920.0,
      "end_time": 335820.0,
      "text": "the boss about my new project."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 336100.0,
      "end_time": 337700.0,
      "text": "Rob: We also had self-reflection -"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 337780.0,
      "end_time": 340559.0,
